{"tid":1124721,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"5步驟簡單訓練兔子去廁所 (美國兔協的建議!)","createTime":"2019-04-25T08:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T08:34:19.000Z","uid":197098,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c5104f64a7a47fe723af2cc9829786a156e8fc79","tid":1124721,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>5個步驟</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 請買貓廁所(Cat-sized Litterbox)給你家的兔子(要有足夠空間給兔子360度移動)，市面上的兔子廁所實在太細，只適合龍貓、天竺鼠等小動物。貓廁所會讓你的兔子開心和舒適地跳入去使用，亦會減少𥚃面的墊材和糞便跌出來，更加乾淨。廁所內一半放乾草(Hay)，一半放墊材。一至兩天換一次，視乎有多骯髒:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1rwxt5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1rwxt5.jpg&h=aa4143da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廁所有蓋或沒有蓋也可以, 例如：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6wsQfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6wsQfS.jpg&h=105669ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQsS1ny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQsS1ny.jpg&h=49ecb059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 訓練兔子￼去廁所是很簡單。糞便是沒有臭味，而且是乾，容易清理。兔子在籠裡大便是正常的，是表示這個籠是牠的地盤 (但牠會知道litterbox是牠的廁所，大部分糞便會在litterbox內排泄😊)。開始的時候在籠內和加一個小空間內走動(圍欄圍住)，將廁所放在籠或圍欄內，然後逐漸地加一點範圍。不要一開始就讓牠在整個家周圍走，這樣會比較難適應。當你給牠的空間越來越大，可以加多一兩個廁所在牠喜歡去大小便的牆角使用。<br />\n<br />\n3. 將隨地的大便放回廁所內，以及隨地的小便用墊材(例如Carefresh)抹完放入廁所內，牠便會知道要在廁所內大小便(所以美國兔協說其實不需要訓練😇)。每次牠在廁所內大小便，就給他零食作獎勵。選擇獎勵，不要懲罰。記住不要打兔子，牠們與狗和貓不同，如果打，牠永遠不會忘記，令到與主人關係和信任差。壓力(stress) 亦可以會令兔子生病。兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(predator)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。他們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會驚嚇兔子。當牠們受驚時，groom(撫摸和親吻)牠們是很重要，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。<br />\n<br />\n4. 當然，兔子要絕育才可容易訓練去廁所，因為霸地盤(territorial marker), 絕育後會大大減少霸地盤。荷爾蒙減少了也會令攻擊性減少，牠會活得更開心。專家說絕育後才看到兔子的真正本性，例如: 善良、懶惰、好動、活潑、親人......(有些兔子活潑和親人，有些善良但懶惰等等)另外，兔子是很容易患上生殖器疾病的動物，所以絕育也會令牠們更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 記住要有耐心: 有些兔子比較快, 有些比較慢。當然，有時候牠們不開心不聽話或者些少霸地盤原因也會隨地大便。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 也有教, 步驟簡單:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rg1RlhtXV7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRg1RlhtXV7A&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=fc6907bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rg1RlhtXV7A</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>墊材</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n記住不要買松木、雪松木及紅杉木的木屑(Pine shavings &amp; Cedar Shavings)，因為有種化學物質叫酚(Aromatic Phenols)會傷兔子的肝臟。Pine pellets或其他墊材就沒問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">買的時候最好看清楚英文名字 ! </span>因為依然有很多寵物店售賣這類型的墊材。<br />\n<br />\n總括來說，以下的墊材是對兔子<strong><ins>有害</ins></strong>：<br />\n1. Pine shavings and cedar shavings<br />\n2. Clay/Clumping litter<br />\n3. Corn cob litter<br />\n4. Scented litter<br />\n5. Newspaper / Shredded paper<br />\n<br />\n以下是對兔子<strong><ins>安全</ins></strong>：<br />\n1. Paper pulp, 即是Carefresh (推介! 兔子吃了也沒問題因為消化得到然後排出來)<br />\n2. Compressed newspaper<br />\n3. Compressed sawdust pellets, 即是 Feline Pine, Wood stove pellets, Horse stall pellets <br />\n<br />\n更多關於兔子去廁所的資訊(美國兔子協會): <a href=\"https://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=9a1c22f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org</a>"},{"pid":"35a92f4261b64665c325f8d516ad3e2b1168ab9e","tid":1124721,"uid":24390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"@狗強"},{"pid":"52be423580bec3c0d7df0750dae620ae58177c37","tid":1124721,"uid":7064,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdJSgXs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdJSgXs.png&h=ba8b13b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f31d1bf79602fc05f89962fd79b921f5ce2d601","tid":1124721,"uid":706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"想請教下各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兔仔使唔使人陪 (如果屋企日頭無人，去哂返工，得夜晚先返)<br />\n痴唔痴人？<br />\n平時除左摸下抱下仲有無咩互動？可以分享下你地養兔仔既感覺嗎？<br />\n去兔協睇過，好多都係有肝病同眼有事(無記錯的話)，係咪兔仔容易有依方面問題，定係多數人飼養方式出錯搞到咁？<br />\n唔該各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82862aa5bccc6e9f4bb59754f366fa7ba4cebd63","tid":1124721,"uid":7064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f31d1bf79602fc05f89962fd79b921f5ce2d601","tid":1124721,"uid":706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"想請教下各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兔仔使唔使人陪 (如果屋企日頭無人，去哂返工，得夜晚先返)<br />\n痴唔痴人？<br />\n平時除左摸下抱下仲有無咩互動？可以分享下你地養兔仔既感覺嗎？<br />\n去兔協睇過，好多都係有肝病同眼有事(無記錯的話)，係咪兔仔容易有依方面問題，定係多數人飼養方式出錯搞到咁？<br />\n唔該各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:13:10.000Z","msg":"出門前放多小小糧 草<br />\n返到去放佢出來等佢郁動下<br />\n摸多啲佢個頭 隻兔慣咗你浸味之後<br />\n再試下放隻手去佢下爬到<br />\n嘗試下隻兔瘋狂奶你隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兔無記錯約莫8-12個月大就要帶佢絕育<br />\n如果唔係遲下好大機會生癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccf57a327468bb48fed3b7fe599bfc13d8f6c2a","tid":1124721,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52be423580bec3c0d7df0750dae620ae58177c37","tid":1124721,"uid":7064,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdJSgXs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdJSgXs.png&h=ba8b13b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:38:10.000Z","msg":"可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacd48574c08a3402dfedaf3fc51f395c7200b90","tid":1124721,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7f31d1bf79602fc05f89962fd79b921f5ce2d601","tid":1124721,"uid":706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"想請教下各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兔仔使唔使人陪 (如果屋企日頭無人，去哂返工，得夜晚先返)<br />\n痴唔痴人？<br />\n平時除左摸下抱下仲有無咩互動？可以分享下你地養兔仔既感覺嗎？<br />\n去兔協睇過，好多都係有肝病同眼有事(無記錯的話)，係咪兔仔容易有依方面問題，定係多數人飼養方式出錯搞到咁？<br />\n唔該各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:41:28.000Z","msg":"兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n有很多人以為兔子無視主人而棄養，其實是誤會：兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n以下2個videos可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=fb8299cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=a40e6c4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a> <br />\n<br />\n兔子的行為解釋網站：<br />\n<br />\n香港兔協: <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=7155816e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a> <br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站): <a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=7cfb051a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a> <br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂): <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=a4a8bba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"436bc26f5ececdbb2048d256dd499c7638b6b087","tid":1124721,"uid":706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aacd48574c08a3402dfedaf3fc51f395c7200b90","tid":1124721,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7f31d1bf79602fc05f89962fd79b921f5ce2d601","tid":1124721,"uid":706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"想請教下各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兔仔使唔使人陪 (如果屋企日頭無人，去哂返工，得夜晚先返)<br />\n痴唔痴人？<br />\n平時除左摸下抱下仲有無咩互動？可以分享下你地養兔仔既感覺嗎？<br />\n去兔協睇過，好多都係有肝病同眼有事(無記錯的話)，係咪兔仔容易有依方面問題，定係多數人飼養方式出錯搞到咁？<br />\n唔該各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:41:28.000Z","msg":"兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n有很多人以為兔子無視主人而棄養，其實是誤會：兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n以下2個videos可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=fb8299cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=a40e6c4a\" data-auto-